evels ... </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> lower levels mean increased aggro range of mobs...<br><br>  limit all lower levels to last groups.. sorry, it might not seem fair, but its just the way it has to be<br><br>---<br>a main advasary was LD..  man, we lost too many people over and over again... including myself.. and ther eis nothing you can do against that<br>---<br>,,, alot of the raid depends on people listening in generall and making sure they do what they have to , even if it means their own death...<br><br>.and that leads us to this problem... toniight  training the camp was a problem ..... if your sowed, you can have aggro, and not know it.. and pull three mobs or more right to camp <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br>i tried ot emphasise the importance of looking back and making sure your not being followed or agroed before comming to camp...   next time i will double my efforts  to educate people...<br><br>otherwise  everyone was very nice and polite and listened as best they could..  i had a fun time, and sometimes you learn more from failures...<br><br>no loot to report.. or sure some stuff dropped, but not much and in the  horrific mess that was 'break-in' i didnt write anything down ...<br><br>another final note...   for gods sake.. i was BOMBARDED WITH TELLS  the first three hours of the raid ..... this is another reason all my raids will be SIGN UP ONLY  from now on...<br><br>i hope people won't judge my raiding soley on this one raid.. but  rather call it the bottom of my bell curve , lol ..<br><br>and again<br>thanks soooo much to the poeple from TSW who helped us.   and thanks to the poeple from the other guilds who came and helped <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>and thanks to Yizelar for helping me coordinate things.<br><br>and thanks to all our main and 2nd assist. and to our pullers...  who ever you were through out the night .. we changed more often them mobs we killed i think! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br>anywho ... *sigh* <br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>   sing with me!!<br><br>*singing* ya take the good..<br>ya take the bad..<br>ya add 'em up and there ya have<br>..the Facts of Life...<br>.....the Facts of Life!! *weee*<br></i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br><br><br><br><br>peace and love <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br>Destructress Fryestarter <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>-- <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udestructressfyrestarter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Destructress Fyrestarter</A> at: 4/5/02 3:06:19 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uabraxis215.showPublicProfile?language=EN>abraxis215</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(4/5/02 2:56:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscogplanesraidschedule.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=248.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Plane of Fear recap </span><hr size=1> It wasn't too bad, a lot of dying but that happens, <br>maybe I'm strange but I thought the whole experience was<br>kind of funny heehee. Even when the dracoliche dropped me<br>when I overagroed after the MT went down <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :o --><img src=http://www.e